      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.Dysu4F8licjEb2FY]{Vanguard Discipline}</p>\n<p>Once per day, you can spend 3 Entropy points to make a full attack as a standard action. In addition, you and up to six allies within 30 feet are affected by @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.spells.Item.PecEOjojT15BJKi9]{Haste} (Core Rulebook 358) for 1 minute after you use this ability, with the extra speed from the haste effect increased to 60 feet (to a maximum of three times the creature’s normal speed). These effects don’t stack with similar effects.</p>"
